739
01:19:15.809 --> 01:19:16.809
Bell.

740
01:19:19.855 --> 01:19:20.855
Bell.

741
01:19:30.824 --> 01:19:31.533
Bell.

742
01:19:31.742 --> 01:19:32.368
Detente.

743
01:19:32.409 --> 01:19:33.077
Bell.

744
01:19:33.118 --> 01:19:33.786
Dije que te detuvieras.

745
01:19:33.869 --> 01:19:34.869
Bell.

746
01:19:35.204 --> 01:19:36.204
Detente.

747
01:19:40.667 --> 01:19:41.667
Bell.

748
01:19:41.960 --> 01:19:42.544
Bell.

749
01:19:42.544 --> 01:19:43.544
Detente.

750
01:19:43.629 --> 01:19:44.629
Bell.

751
